<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣- أَلَمْ نُهْلِكِ الْأَوَّلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٦)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ثُمَّ نُتْبِعُهُمُ الْآخِرِينَ <span class="c2">(١٧)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>كَذلِكَ نَفْعَلُ بِالْمُجْرِمِينَ <span class="c2">(١٨)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِلْمُكَذِّبِينَ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٥٤- إِنَّ الَّذِينَ أَجْرَمُوا كانُوا مِنَ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا يَضْحَكُونَ <span class="c2">(٢٩)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَإِذا مَرُّوا بِهِمْ يَتَغامَزُونَ <span class="c2">(٣٠)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَإِذَا انْقَلَبُوا إِلى أَهْلِهِمُ انْقَلَبُوا فَكِهِينَ <span class="c2">(٣١)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَإِذا رَأَوْهُمْ قالُوا إِنَّ هؤُلاءِ لَضالُّونَ <span class="c2">(٣٢)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَما أُرْسِلُوا عَلَيْهِمْ حافِظِينَ <span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
